data.description: Great 4 bed 2 bath in Little Creek subdivision. This patio home abuts green space with no homes behind it. Covered patio, front porch, 2 car garage, split floor plan and not a pass through street keeping this neighborhood quiet! This home has had one owner! and he has maintained it through the years he's owned it. Close to NAS, Exchange, PX, Navy hospital, beaches, shopping, downtown and everything you could need!
